---
import Value from "../base/Value.astro";

import always_open from "../../assets/images/values-always-open.png";
import optimizing_impact from "../../assets/images/values-optimizing-impact.png";
import simplicity from "../../assets/images/values-simplicity.png";
import teachers_not_technocrats from "../../assets/images/values-teachers-not-technocrats.png";
import teams_not_hierarchies from "../../assets/images/values-teams-not-hierarchies.png";
---

<div class="flex items-center justify-center bg-base-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl px-12 lg:px-0">
    <h1 class="py-8 text-left text-4xl text-secondary">Our values</h1>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 md:gap-4">
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <Value
          title="Optimizing for impact"
          image={{
            src: optimizing_impact,
            alt: "Optimizing impact",
          }}
        >
          <Fragment slot="content">
            Time is precious, and there is a lot of need out there. We are
            intentional about whom we help and how. To maximize our impact in
            the space, we need to be conscientious allies to a diverse
            community.
          </Fragment>
        </Value>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <Value
          title="Teachers not technocrats"
          image={{
            src: teachers_not_technocrats,
            alt: "Teachers not technocrats",
          }}
        >
          <Fragment slot="content">
            Weâ€™re not trying to impress anyone with our sophistication. We want
            to empower our clients through mentorship, guidance, and by
            fostering a mentality of self-service.
          </Fragment>
        </Value>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <Value
          title="Simplicity"
          image={{
            src: simplicity,
            alt: "Simplicity",
          }}
        >
          <Fragment slot="content">
            We strive for simple, effective, and sustainable solutions that
            empower our clients to focus on their domain expertise, not maintain
            our contribution.
          </Fragment>
        </Value>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <Value
          title="Always open"
          image={{
            src: always_open,
            alt: "Always open",
          }}
        >
          <Fragment slot="content">
            When we build tools, we are intentional about open source licensing,
            and encourage our collaborators to act in kind. We promote financial
            transparency and collaboration.
          </Fragment>
        </Value>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-4">
        <Value
          title="Teams not hierarchies"
          image={{
            src: teams_not_hierarchies,
            alt: "Teams not hierarchies",
          }}
        >
          <Fragment slot="content">
            At CSI, we believe innovation and creativity come from tightly
            collaborative, self-sufficient teams.
          </Fragment>
        </Value>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
